======================================================================
dc5 CANCELLATION MECHANISM AT n=8
======================================================================

Subset S = [1, 4, 5, 6]
S scores: (np.int64(1), np.int64(1), np.int64(2), np.int64(2))

Arcs within S (before -> after):
  4->1 becomes 1->4
  1->5 becomes 5->1
  1->6 becomes 6->1
  5->4 becomes 4->5
  6->4 becomes 4->6
  5->6 becomes 6->5

